  "informal_statement": "The number of pairs in the Cartesian product of two finite sets equals the product of their individual sizes — the fundamental counting principle.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Finset.card_product`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem card_product' (s t : Finset ℕ) : (s ×ˢ t).card = s.card * t.card",
